The changes to this repo are attempting to make zigbee publish mqtt
just like esphome does.

To publish the changes:
 1. Build an image: docker build . --file docker/Dockerfile --tag krconv/zigbee2mqtt-amd64:1.21.2-1
 2. Push the image from the Docker Desktop app
 3. Use the custom repo that poinnts to the docker tag: https://github.com/krconv/hassio-zigbee2mqtt
